msgid ""
"With TaxoPress Pro, you can duplicate taxonomy terms along with all their "
"metadata. This includes term descriptions, images, and custom fields. You "
"can copy terms between taxonomies to maintain consistent organization "
"across your site."
msgstr ""
"Dengan TaxoPress Pro, Anda dapat menduplikasi istilah taksonomi beserta "
"semua metadata mereka. Ini termasuk deskripsi istilah, gambar, dan bidang "
"kustom. Anda dapat menyalin istilah antar taksonomi untuk menjaga "
"organisasi yang konsisten di seluruh situs Anda."

#: includes-core/TaxopressCoreAdmin.php:734
msgid ""
